          "description": "Dr. Daniel Kim has a great bedside manner and is one of the few doctors who truly takes the time to educate his patients and discuss ideas about their care. That level of attention is rare and very much appreciated.\nYilin, the tech, is also excellent\u2014professional, kind, and efficient. I\u2019ve been coming here for years for my annual check-ups, and every visit is seamless: on time, quick, and efficient without sacrificing quality care. Highly recommend. \u2b50",
