          "description": "I had a physical exam. Dr. Daniel Kim was very thorough and supportive. He spent time going over recent medical reports.  He advised me to follow up with a cardiologist.\nThe additional staff members Yilin, Ciara and Alberto were pleasant, professional and explained the necessary procedures as part of the exam protocol.",
