          "description": "Dr Kim is an excellent primary care physician. Thoughtful, attentive, and highly knowledgeable. Appointments are thorough without feeling rushed, and communication is clear and professional. I consistently feel well cared for and confident in the medical guidance provided. Highly recommend.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkelJIbEZhbVJRTmt3eVZYWmlVVTlpVDFOVWEwRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x25e4f724faca6735!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOldzRHlFamRQNkwyVXZiUU9iT1NUa0E%7C%7C?hl=en",
