          "description": "I found this office on ZocDoc while searching for a new provider for my annual physical. I don\u2019t have any major health concerns (thank Gd), so I just needed a place that was convenient and accepted my insurance (United Healthcare). This clinic checked all the boxes!\n\nThe front desk staff was very kind, and my provider, Hannah Cohan, NP, was great \u2014 very thorough and attentive during the exam.\n\nWhat really stood out to me, though, was how beautiful the clinic is. From the modern architecture to the stunning finishes and fixtures, everything felt clean, calming, and thoughtfully designed from the lobby to the exam rooms. It\u2019s probably the nicest medical office I\u2019ve ever been in.\n\nHighly recommend for anyone looking for a regular Doctor/Nurse Practitioner in a beautiful, professional setting!",
